4:
After the lightning flashes, we hear the thunder,\q2 which is like God's powerful voice;
\q2 when he speaks, he does not keep back the lightning.
\q1

21:
You know that people cannot look directly at the sun\q2 when it shines brightly in the sky after the wind has blown the clouds away;
\q2 likewise we certainly cannot look at the brightness of God.
\q1
